            "text": "—Heb., ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "and as for the iron, it fell.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " The subject of the verb is made prominent by being put first in the accusative. It is thus implied that something ",
