        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). They probably acquired a knowledge of the smelting process in Egypt, where iron was employed at least from the time of the third Rameses. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
